WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:00:32.800 --> 00:00:34.280
Good evening, players.

00:00:34.760 --> 00:00:35.840
I am today's host.

00:00:36.560 --> 00:00:38.800
Today's script is Death's Descent.

00:00:39.280 --> 00:00:40.240
In this story,

00:00:40.560 --> 00:00:41.400
you will play

00:00:41.520 --> 00:00:42.560
different roles.

00:00:43.120 --> 00:00:43.880
The game

00:00:44.160 --> 00:00:45.160
starts.

00:00:56.280 --> 00:00:57.080
Energy drink.

00:00:57.840 --> 00:00:58.640
Seven points.

00:01:00.720 --> 00:01:01.920
Give me three points.

00:01:04.640 --> 00:01:05.770
The points are mine.

00:01:06.240 --> 00:01:07.040
Seven points.

00:01:07.480 --> 00:01:08.200
One prop.

00:01:13.039 --> 00:01:15.039
Lin Ran is pregnant with Xu Xing's child.

00:01:15.039 --> 00:01:16.500
Xu Xing bought her a house.

00:01:24.600 --> 00:01:25.080
Xiaoru.

00:01:25.560 --> 00:01:27.960
Stop playing on your phone. It's your turn.

00:01:33.039 --> 00:01:35.240
Go to hell, you shameless homewrecker!

00:01:36.240 --> 00:01:37.770
Xiaoru, what are you doing?

00:01:38.560 --> 00:01:40.090
Is this part in your script?

00:01:40.640 --> 00:01:42.900
Even if it is, you can't actually hit her!

00:01:43.880 --> 00:01:44.810
What do you know?

00:01:44.960 --> 00:01:47.360
It's called truly listening, looking, and feeling.

00:01:47.360 --> 00:01:49.820
It's the basic professionalism of an actor.

00:01:51.240 --> 00:01:52.360
Not bad, Xiaoru.

00:01:52.800 --> 00:01:55.130
Your acting is getting better and better.

00:01:55.800 --> 00:01:57.039
Then, is Mr. Xu interested

00:01:57.039 --> 00:01:58.570
in investing in my new show?

00:01:59.320 --> 00:01:59.800
Sure.

00:02:00.200 --> 00:02:01.330
I'll think about it.

00:02:06.400 --> 00:02:06.860
Come on.

00:02:07.400 --> 00:02:08.060
Keep going.

00:02:15.560 --> 00:02:16.420
Pick two cards.

00:02:17.320 --> 00:02:18.180
Double points.

00:02:20.240 --> 00:02:21.240
Strength potion.

00:02:22.200 --> 00:02:23.060
Poison for you.

00:02:23.720 --> 00:02:24.850
I have the antidote.

00:02:40.800 --> 00:02:41.400
Game

00:02:42.200 --> 00:02:42.920
over.

00:02:50.040 --> 00:02:52.370
I think this script is quite interesting.

00:02:52.600 --> 00:02:53.800
You were the last one to finish.

00:02:53.800 --> 00:02:55.560
Of course you think it's interesting.

00:02:55.560 --> 00:02:55.880
Exactly.

00:02:55.880 --> 00:02:56.520
Unlike me,

00:02:56.960 --> 00:02:58.640
who died right at the beginning.

00:02:58.640 --> 00:02:59.170
Exactly.

00:02:59.440 --> 00:03:01.040
I think this script has a plot hole.

00:03:01.040 --> 00:03:02.600
Logically, I have the highest IQ.

00:03:02.600 --> 00:03:04.080
I should be the one to survive until the end.

00:03:04.080 --> 00:03:06.040
You're just a scumbag in this.

00:03:06.360 --> 00:03:08.320
I was so good to you, yet you betrayed me.

00:03:08.320 --> 00:03:08.650
Well,

00:03:09.360 --> 00:03:10.920
you guys weren't any better.

00:03:10.920 --> 00:03:11.920
The setting of this script

00:03:11.920 --> 00:03:13.580
is that everyone is a villain.

00:03:13.920 --> 00:03:14.520
All right.

00:03:14.600 --> 00:03:15.160
Let's go.

00:03:16.160 --> 00:03:17.240
Wenbing, you take Xiaoru home.

00:03:17.240 --> 00:03:18.240
I'll take Lin Ran.

00:03:19.160 --> 00:03:19.560
Well,

00:03:20.400 --> 00:03:21.760
you and Lin Ran aren't going the same way.

00:03:21.760 --> 00:03:23.020
Why are you taking her?

00:03:23.880 --> 00:03:24.880
Because I want to.

00:03:27.000 --> 00:03:27.530
Let's go.

00:03:29.560 --> 00:03:29.920
Oh.

00:03:30.160 --> 00:03:31.160
By the way, Xiaoru,

00:03:31.160 --> 00:03:32.280
I forgot to tell you.

00:03:32.280 --> 00:03:33.280
I recently moved.

00:03:33.400 --> 00:03:34.600
Once I'm all settled,

00:03:34.640 --> 00:03:35.840
I'll invite you over.

00:03:37.200 --> 00:03:38.530
I'll look forward to it.

00:03:46.040 --> 00:03:46.500
Coming.

00:03:49.640 --> 00:03:50.170
Who is it?

00:03:51.920 --> 00:03:52.760
Xiaoru.

00:03:53.320 --> 00:03:53.800
What?

00:03:53.880 --> 00:03:54.810
Am I not welcome?

00:03:55.920 --> 00:03:56.720
Of course not.

00:03:56.920 --> 00:03:57.520
Come on in.

00:03:59.280 --> 00:03:59.540
Wow.

00:04:00.040 --> 00:04:00.700
It's so big.

00:04:01.440 --> 00:04:01.770
Yeah.

00:04:02.080 --> 00:04:02.480
Take a seat.

00:04:02.480 --> 00:04:03.560
Let me get you a glass of water.

00:04:03.560 --> 00:04:04.440
No need.

00:04:04.440 --> 00:04:05.640
Show me around first.

00:04:05.920 --> 00:04:06.560
Sure.

00:04:07.640 --> 00:04:08.700
This is my kitchen.

00:04:09.200 --> 00:04:10.040
Do you cook?

00:04:10.600 --> 00:04:11.280
No.

00:04:11.680 --> 00:04:12.960
I hired a maid.

00:04:12.960 --> 00:04:14.360
Wow, making good money.

00:04:15.320 --> 00:04:16.600
This is the dining table.

00:04:16.600 --> 00:04:17.720
We'll eat here later.

00:04:17.720 --> 00:04:18.000
Okay.

00:04:18.000 --> 00:04:18.560
How is it?

00:04:18.839 --> 00:04:20.170
There's a second floor.

00:04:20.560 --> 00:04:21.079
Let's go.

00:04:21.079 --> 00:04:22.880
I'll take you up to see my bedroom.

00:04:22.880 --> 00:04:23.520
Let's see.

00:04:33.440 --> 00:04:33.840
Hey.

00:04:34.400 --> 00:04:36.400
Why are the stair railings removed?

00:04:37.400 --> 00:04:39.200
This staircase used to be metal.

00:04:39.200 --> 00:04:40.840
In Feng Shui, it easily creates negative energy.

00:04:40.840 --> 00:04:42.200
So I changed it to wood.

00:04:42.840 --> 00:04:42.920
Really?

00:04:42.920 --> 00:04:44.720
Oh, is it?

00:04:44.720 --> 00:04:45.840
You need to replace them quickly.

00:04:45.840 --> 00:04:46.920
It's so dangerous.

00:04:47.040 --> 00:04:48.600
We're just two sections short.

00:04:48.600 --> 00:04:50.200
You still need to be careful.

00:04:50.280 --> 00:04:50.810
Let's go.

00:04:52.600 --> 00:04:53.800
Is this your bedroom?

00:04:53.840 --> 00:04:54.120
Yes.

00:04:54.240 --> 00:04:55.000
Such a big bed.

00:04:55.000 --> 00:04:56.130
Go in and take a look.

00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:08.800
Police!

00:05:09.240 --> 00:05:10.570
I want to report a crime.

00:05:18.680 --> 00:05:20.440
Have you notified the homeowner?

00:05:20.440 --> 00:05:22.900
I called him right after I called the police.

00:05:22.920 --> 00:05:23.760
Mr. Xu said

00:05:23.920 --> 00:05:25.920
he's with clients at the golf course

00:05:26.080 --> 00:05:27.010
and will be late.

00:05:28.480 --> 00:05:29.880
This Mr. Xu is quite busy.

00:05:31.000 --> 00:05:32.440
When were these stairs removed?

00:05:32.440 --> 00:05:33.100
Yesterday.

00:05:33.320 --> 00:05:34.120
Just removed.

00:05:35.800 --> 00:05:36.960
The renovation company said

00:05:36.960 --> 00:05:39.000
they can finish installing it tomorrow.

00:05:39.000 --> 00:05:39.860
I didn't expect

00:05:40.000 --> 00:05:40.600
that today

00:05:40.640 --> 00:05:42.100
an accident would happen.

00:05:42.560 --> 00:05:42.720
Captain Gu.

00:05:42.720 --> 00:05:43.850
What a coincidence.

00:05:45.960 --> 00:05:46.620
Have a seat.

00:05:47.040 --> 00:05:48.040
Don't be nervous.

00:07:00.840 --> 00:07:02.240
The victim's footprints

00:07:02.480 --> 00:07:04.740
were first pointing towards the stairs,

00:07:04.760 --> 00:07:06.620
then turned towards the bedroom.

00:07:09.200 --> 00:07:10.880
There are wiping marks here.

00:07:12.040 --> 00:07:14.370
There must be a second person at the scene.

00:07:23.000 --> 00:07:24.530
Looking at the footprints,

00:07:24.800 --> 00:07:26.860
they fell down the stairs backwards.

00:07:28.280 --> 00:07:30.740
There might have been a scuffle at the scene.

00:07:52.960 --> 00:07:54.760
There are wiping marks here too.

00:07:55.920 --> 00:07:59.720
The killer wore the victim's slippers to create a false impression.

00:08:10.000 --> 00:08:10.530
Exactly.

00:08:13.160 --> 00:08:15.360
It's a carefully fabricated accident.

00:08:19.760 --> 00:08:20.360
Master.

00:08:24.520 --> 00:08:25.840
The neighborhood surveillance shows

00:08:25.840 --> 00:08:27.970
that a woman came here this afternoon.

00:08:35.520 --> 00:08:36.720
I checked the surveillance.

00:08:36.720 --> 00:08:38.080
That woman's name is Li Xiaoru.

00:08:38.080 --> 00:08:40.010
I've already sent you her address.

00:08:41.440 --> 00:08:42.000
What?

00:08:43.039 --> 00:08:44.080
Lin Ran is dead?

00:08:45.160 --> 00:08:45.620
This...

00:08:46.320 --> 00:08:47.320
How could this be?

00:08:48.960 --> 00:08:50.420
Ranran was still so young.

00:08:51.280 --> 00:08:52.940
She was even expecting a baby.

00:08:54.840 --> 00:08:55.960
When did you leave?

00:08:57.240 --> 00:08:58.360
Around 2:30 p.m.,

00:08:59.360 --> 00:09:00.480
right as I left,

00:09:01.440 --> 00:09:01.920
she was calling

00:09:01.920 --> 00:09:03.320
the renovation company,

00:09:03.960 --> 00:09:05.690
discussing the stair railing.

00:09:06.160 --> 00:09:07.760
She was perfectly fine then.

00:09:08.840 --> 00:09:10.370
Where did you go after that?

00:09:10.720 --> 00:09:11.520
After that...

00:09:12.560 --> 00:09:14.400
I've had a toothache these past two days.

00:09:14.400 --> 00:09:15.800
After leaving her place,

00:09:15.880 --> 00:09:17.140
I went to the hospital.

00:09:17.200 --> 00:09:18.000
The hospital?

00:09:19.080 --> 00:09:20.600
Do you have the registration slip?

00:09:20.600 --> 00:09:21.040
Yes.

00:09:21.640 --> 00:09:22.840
I'll go get it for you.

00:09:48.400 --> 00:09:49.000
All right.

00:09:49.280 --> 00:09:50.480
We'll get going then.

00:09:50.760 --> 00:09:52.200
We'll take this receipt back with us.

00:09:52.200 --> 00:09:53.600
Don't leave Jiangcheng for now.

00:09:53.600 --> 00:09:54.000
Okay.

00:09:54.840 --> 00:09:55.400
Let's go.

00:10:05.600 --> 00:10:06.730
How did I do just now?

00:10:07.600 --> 00:10:08.120
Not bad.

00:10:09.960 --> 00:10:10.600
That's all

00:10:10.600 --> 00:10:12.400
thanks to our great Lawyer Zhao.

00:10:12.800 --> 00:10:15.060
I'll have to thank you properly tonight.

00:10:15.560 --> 00:10:17.160
How are you going to thank me?

00:10:18.280 --> 00:10:19.560
Li Xiaoru's acting

00:10:20.160 --> 00:10:21.280
is way too obvious.

00:10:22.040 --> 00:10:23.440
All the props were set up,

00:10:23.600 --> 00:10:25.600
just waiting for us to investigate.

00:10:25.920 --> 00:10:28.040
Plus, there was someone else in her house.

00:10:28.040 --> 00:10:28.760
A man.

00:10:29.680 --> 00:10:30.880
Her story

00:10:30.880 --> 00:10:32.340
and the hospital receipts

00:10:32.920 --> 00:10:34.920
were probably prepared by that man.

00:10:36.640 --> 00:10:38.360
And judging from the nightstand,

00:10:38.360 --> 00:10:41.240
and the torn condom wrapper,

00:10:42.400 --> 00:10:44.260
that man must be very close to her.

00:10:54.160 --> 00:10:54.960
Hey, Boss.

00:10:55.040 --> 00:10:57.840
The male owner of the apartment finally showed up.

00:10:58.040 --> 00:10:58.770
Understood.

00:11:15.000 --> 00:11:15.240
Oh.

00:11:15.400 --> 00:11:16.060
No, thanks.

00:11:20.440 --> 00:11:21.240
I am Xu Xing.

00:11:21.960 --> 00:11:22.560
This house

00:11:22.720 --> 00:11:23.200
is mine.

00:11:25.040 --> 00:11:27.240
What is your relationship with Lin Ran?

00:11:29.240 --> 00:11:30.040
Her?

00:11:31.120 --> 00:11:32.080
I guess I'm her

00:11:32.680 --> 00:11:33.360
boyfriend.

00:11:41.640 --> 00:11:43.570
What's going on with these stairs?

00:11:46.280 --> 00:11:48.080
I told her not to mess with these stairs,

00:11:48.080 --> 00:11:49.480
but she wouldn't listen.

00:11:49.800 --> 00:11:51.920
This is a fully furnished house from the developer.

00:11:51.920 --> 00:11:52.640
Before,

00:11:52.640 --> 00:11:53.440
there was a

00:11:53.760 --> 00:11:54.620
metal railing.

00:11:55.640 --> 00:11:58.300
She said the metal railing ruined the Feng Shui.

00:11:58.840 --> 00:11:59.600
Now look,

00:12:00.400 --> 00:12:01.330
the baby is gone,

00:12:01.560 --> 00:12:03.200
and this house is haunted.

00:12:04.520 --> 00:12:05.580
At a time like this,

00:12:05.920 --> 00:12:08.250
he only cares about the house and the baby.

00:12:09.080 --> 00:12:09.640
Officer,

00:12:10.960 --> 00:12:12.090
what I lack the least

00:12:12.240 --> 00:12:13.400
is women.

00:12:20.840 --> 00:12:22.040
Do you know this girl?

00:12:23.440 --> 00:12:23.800
Yes.

00:12:24.520 --> 00:12:25.380
It's Li Xiaoru.

00:12:26.160 --> 00:12:27.240
Look closely again,

00:12:27.240 --> 00:12:27.970
and confirm.

00:12:29.600 --> 00:12:30.280
Officer,

00:12:31.080 --> 00:12:32.410
a woman I've slept with,

00:12:33.200 --> 00:12:34.530
how could I not know her?

00:12:36.280 --> 00:12:38.280
What's the relationship between the three of you?

00:12:38.280 --> 00:12:39.880
We were college classmates.

00:12:40.880 --> 00:12:41.960
I don't smoke, thanks.

00:12:41.960 --> 00:12:42.360
Here.

00:12:45.240 --> 00:12:47.900
We were hanging out together just a few days ago.

00:12:50.160 --> 00:12:51.360
Li Xiaoru and Lin Ran

00:12:51.480 --> 00:12:52.940
were kind of best friends.

00:12:53.240 --> 00:12:55.170
But they competed a lot privately.

00:12:55.320 --> 00:12:56.250
Women, you know.

00:12:56.320 --> 00:12:58.250
It's always about the same things.

00:12:59.320 --> 00:13:01.250
I suspect Li Xiaoru killed Lin Ran.

00:13:04.800 --> 00:13:05.320
Why?

00:13:06.600 --> 00:13:07.280
Because

00:13:07.640 --> 00:13:08.370
of jealousy.

00:13:09.520 --> 00:13:10.720
In college,

00:13:10.720 --> 00:13:11.920
Li Xiaoru and I dated.

00:13:12.240 --> 00:13:13.300
Not long ago, I just

00:13:13.640 --> 00:13:15.100
got together with Lin Ran.

00:13:15.760 --> 00:13:18.020
Lin Ran even told me not to tell Li Xiaoru.

00:13:18.840 --> 00:13:20.440
It seems Li Xiaoru found out.

00:13:29.400 --> 00:13:31.000
This girl would kill someone

00:13:31.560 --> 00:13:32.760
just out of jealousy?

00:13:33.160 --> 00:13:33.800
Officer,

00:13:34.280 --> 00:13:35.680
you don't know Li Xiaoru,

00:13:35.840 --> 00:13:36.600
but I do.

00:13:37.160 --> 00:13:37.800
Knowing her personality,

00:13:37.800 --> 00:13:39.640
she is definitely capable of doing something like this.

00:13:39.640 --> 00:13:40.600
Back in college,

00:13:40.600 --> 00:13:42.040
she was the bossy girl in school.

00:13:42.040 --> 00:13:43.900
She bullied anyone she disliked.

00:13:44.440 --> 00:13:46.800
She got even worse after becoming an actress.

00:13:46.800 --> 00:13:47.240
Recently,

00:13:47.240 --> 00:13:48.560
a girl took her role,

00:13:49.160 --> 00:13:51.220
and she almost disfigured that girl.

00:13:51.240 --> 00:13:51.770
Besides,

00:13:52.440 --> 00:13:54.320
didn't you check the surveillance?

00:13:54.320 --> 00:13:55.600
Apart from the nanny,

00:13:55.800 --> 00:13:58.400
she was the only one who came here today, right?

00:14:00.440 --> 00:14:01.080
Oh, right,

00:14:01.640 --> 00:14:03.640
is the baby in Lin Ran's belly yours?

00:14:04.520 --> 00:14:05.320
That's right.

00:14:05.360 --> 00:14:07.090
Why else would I buy this house?

00:14:07.200 --> 00:14:09.400
To be frank, I was just paying for a womb.

00:14:11.160 --> 00:14:12.160
Back in college,

00:14:12.160 --> 00:14:14.480
Li Xiaoru was also pregnant with my child.

00:14:14.480 --> 00:14:15.540
But I was young then

00:14:16.600 --> 00:14:17.880
and didn't want the baby.

00:14:17.880 --> 00:14:19.080
So I gave her a few bags

00:14:19.960 --> 00:14:21.020
to get an abortion.

00:14:22.040 --> 00:14:22.640
And now?

00:14:23.480 --> 00:14:25.240
If Li Xiaoru knew that I

00:14:25.240 --> 00:14:27.970
bought this house for Lin Ran because of the baby,

00:14:28.240 --> 00:14:29.970
I bet she'd be furious to death.

00:14:37.080 --> 00:14:38.040
Tell me,

00:14:38.640 --> 00:14:40.300
where am I inferior to Lin Ran?

00:14:40.920 --> 00:14:42.480
I just can't figure out

00:14:43.120 --> 00:14:44.760
what Xu Xing sees in Lin Ran.

00:14:46.120 --> 00:14:47.780
Whether it's looks or figure,

00:14:47.800 --> 00:14:49.600
you are much better than Lin Ran.

00:14:49.840 --> 00:14:50.640
Xu Xing

00:14:50.760 --> 00:14:51.760
probably just

00:14:52.320 --> 00:14:53.720
has had too much rich food

00:14:54.440 --> 00:14:56.400
and wants something light for a change.

00:14:56.400 --> 00:14:57.200
Makes sense.

00:14:58.440 --> 00:14:59.300
What about you?

00:14:59.840 --> 00:15:00.900
Why are you with me?

00:15:02.040 --> 00:15:03.920
Don't say it's because you like me.

00:15:03.920 --> 00:15:06.450
I stopped believing that crap a long time ago.

00:15:08.040 --> 00:15:08.920
Have fun while you can.

00:15:08.920 --> 00:15:09.980
Enjoy the present.

00:15:10.440 --> 00:15:12.170
Why do you need so many reasons?

00:15:13.040 --> 00:15:14.360
Is it because I used to

00:15:14.520 --> 00:15:15.840
be Xu Xing's woman?

00:15:19.080 --> 00:15:20.010
What do you mean?

00:15:21.680 --> 00:15:23.080
Don't think I don't know.

00:15:23.120 --> 00:15:24.560
You and his wife, Wang Min,

00:15:24.560 --> 00:15:25.760
are having an affair.

00:15:28.280 --> 00:15:29.540
You looked at my phone?

00:15:31.280 --> 00:15:32.360
I didn't just look,

00:15:33.160 --> 00:15:34.560
I also kept the evidence.

00:15:36.280 --> 00:15:37.080
Zhao Wenbing.

00:15:37.720 --> 00:15:40.180
Do you just like women Xu Xing has slept with?

00:15:40.240 --> 00:15:42.400
Sleeping with his ex-girlfriend wasn't enough,

00:15:42.400 --> 00:15:44.400
you also had to hook up with his wife.

00:15:44.560 --> 00:15:45.160
Nonsense.

00:15:46.600 --> 00:15:48.330
It's just a fling with Wang Min.

00:15:49.240 --> 00:15:49.800
Besides,

00:15:51.640 --> 00:15:53.570
Xu Xing orders me around every day.

00:15:53.840 --> 00:15:54.800
So I fool around with his women.

00:15:54.800 --> 00:15:55.520
What's the problem?

00:15:55.520 --> 00:15:56.720
Just fooling around?

00:15:57.040 --> 00:15:57.760
Dare you say

00:15:58.280 --> 00:16:00.610
you didn't touch the money in his company?

00:16:06.800 --> 00:16:07.160
Yeah.

00:16:08.000 --> 00:16:10.660
He definitely wants me to fix something for him.

00:16:12.520 --> 00:16:12.920
Hello.

00:16:15.800 --> 00:16:16.280
Yeah.

00:16:18.080 --> 00:16:18.680
Okay, I got it.

00:16:18.680 --> 00:16:19.810
I'll be right there.

00:16:22.560 --> 00:16:23.360
Zhao Wenbing.

00:16:23.880 --> 00:16:25.280
With your intelligence,

00:16:25.560 --> 00:16:27.420
why do you have to work for Xu Xing?

00:16:27.520 --> 00:16:28.720
Are you willing to settle for this?

00:16:28.720 --> 00:16:29.520
Of course not.

00:16:30.760 --> 00:16:34.320
How could Han Xin willingly suffer the humiliation of crawling between someone's legs?

00:16:34.320 --> 00:16:34.720
I am enduring this now,

00:16:34.720 --> 00:16:35.850
just for the future.

00:16:36.360 --> 00:16:37.960
Since you have discovered my deployment,

00:16:37.960 --> 00:16:38.760
I'll tell you.

00:16:38.920 --> 00:16:39.920
Xu Xing's things,

00:16:41.680 --> 00:16:42.410
what is mine,

00:16:43.000 --> 00:16:43.660
I will take.

00:16:44.680 --> 00:16:45.610
What is not mine,

00:16:45.680 --> 00:16:46.610
I will also take.

00:16:46.960 --> 00:16:47.960
Just wait and see.

00:16:49.440 --> 00:16:50.970
Why did Xu Xing look for you?

00:16:51.200 --> 00:16:52.400
Could he have guessed

00:16:52.680 --> 00:16:53.840
that I killed Lin Ran?

00:16:53.840 --> 00:16:55.280
Sigh, it's just company business.

00:16:55.280 --> 00:16:56.410
Don't overthink it.

00:16:58.240 --> 00:16:59.040
Zhao Wenbing,

00:17:00.160 --> 00:17:01.090
I'm warning you.

00:17:02.520 --> 00:17:03.320
I hold

00:17:03.680 --> 00:17:05.339
a lot of leverage against you.

00:17:05.760 --> 00:17:07.040
If you dare betray me,

00:17:07.800 --> 00:17:08.859
I won't let you off.

00:17:11.800 --> 00:17:12.440
Relax.

00:17:14.240 --> 00:17:16.300
Lin Ran's death was just an accident.

00:17:16.920 --> 00:17:18.450
It won't cause any trouble.

00:17:19.119 --> 00:17:20.520
After all, he won't care.

00:17:22.520 --> 00:17:23.160
Maybe,

00:17:25.000 --> 00:17:28.200
he's already holding another woman in his arms right now.

00:17:31.760 --> 00:17:32.490
I'm leaving.

00:17:32.960 --> 00:17:33.620
Good night.

00:17:45.040 --> 00:17:47.040
Surveillance footage from Lin Ran's neighborhood shows

00:17:47.040 --> 00:17:48.960
that Li Xiaoru left her house

00:17:48.960 --> 00:17:50.640
at 2:32 PM.

00:17:51.400 --> 00:17:52.720
She said at that time,

00:17:52.720 --> 00:17:55.050
Lin Ran was on the phone with the designer.

00:17:55.240 --> 00:17:56.560
The designer also confirmed

00:17:56.560 --> 00:17:57.640
that the call ended

00:17:57.640 --> 00:17:59.360
at 2:35 PM.

00:18:00.320 --> 00:18:01.520
By this time, Li Xiaoru

00:18:01.520 --> 00:18:04.720
had already arrived at the underground garage of Yonghui Supermarket.

00:18:04.720 --> 00:18:06.680
The time on the receipt she provided

00:18:06.680 --> 00:18:08.000
is 3:28 PM.

00:18:10.960 --> 00:18:12.440
That sounds fine.

00:18:13.160 --> 00:18:14.960
Do you think it wasn't Li Xiaoru?

00:18:15.440 --> 00:18:15.800
Yeah.

00:18:18.160 --> 00:18:19.290
There is a key issue.

00:18:20.160 --> 00:18:21.420
This neighborhood...

00:18:21.880 --> 00:18:23.200
It has surveillance blind spots.